I said. "Stop!"

883
01:24:36.279 --> 01:24:37.405
Put down your weapon!

884
01:24:41.242 --> 01:24:42.077
(GROANS)

885
01:24:46.081 --> 01:24:47.874
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

886
01:24:49.876 --> 01:24:51.669
