978
01:40:35.404 --> 01:40:36.488
Accept it.

979
01:40:37.573 --> 01:40:39.033
(GRUNTING)

980
01:41:16.862 --> 01:41:18.864
(YELLS)

981
01:41:20.157 --> 01:41:22.117
