1017
01:47:01.790 --> 01:47:04.543
NAVIN: If you're brave enough
to change yourself...

1018
01:47:04.584 --> 01:47:05.836
you can change the world.

1019
01:47:06.837 --> 01:47:08.046
Wang Wei.

1020
